						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">nocash wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">The TEST SLOTS test was mainly for seeing PROM Data/CounterOut and Title as hexdumps (on the three screens accordingly). That's no longer needed, too. But the Titles in clean-text (not the hex values) would be interesting, to see which slot maps there. If you plug in three cartridges, their titles should appear, probably in same order as how the slots are numbered. Slot selection is done via a 2bit number (hence 4 slots displayed), the last slot might be empty, garbage, or a mirror to another slot.</div><br />Yep, they were in order of slot 1, 2, and 3 (Super Mario World was in slot 1).<br /><div class="attachtitle">Attachment:</div><div class="attachcontent">
